2.1.14
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">USEPA</ENAMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">1987b</NUMEX>) and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">USEPA</ENAMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">1987c</NUMEX>) adapted the fathead
