<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Lussier et al.</ENAMEX> (<TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1985</TIMEX>) and <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">USEPA</ENAMEX> (<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">1987e</NUMEX>) determined that
