the concentrations may be: (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">1</ENAMEX>) <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">4</NUMEX> times the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">RWC</ENAMEX>, (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">2</ENAMEX>) <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">2</NUMEX> times the
