<ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">BOD</ENAMEX>, or ill effects from metabolic <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">wastes</ENAMEX> from <ENAMEX TYPE="ANIMAL">organisms</ENAMEX> in the
